                            <comment id="14577274" author="gagravarr" created="Mon, 8 Jun 2015 14:43:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This was caused by &lt;tt&gt;node.getElementsByTagName(&quot;parser&quot;)&lt;/tt&gt; checking at all depths, which wasn&apos;t what we needed. Fixed in r1684199 by using a non-recursing &lt;tt&gt;getChildNodes()&lt;/tt&gt; call instead&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14577293" author="hudson" created="Mon, 8 Jun 2015 14:53:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;SUCCESS: Integrated in tika-trunk-jdk1.7 #740 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/tika-trunk-jdk1.7/740/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/tika-trunk-jdk1.7/740/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-1653&quot; title=&quot;Tika config xml shouldn&amp;#39;t read nested parser definitions as top level&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;TIKA-1653&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;TIKA-1653&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Re-do the XML parsing in the Tika Config, so that a parser tag with another inside it doesn&apos;t get accidently duplicated at the top level (nick: &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc/tika/trunk/?view=rev&amp;amp;rev=1684199&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc/tika/trunk/?view=rev&amp;amp;rev=1684199&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;/tika/trunk/tika-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/config/TikaConfig.java&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;/tika/trunk/tika-core/src/test/java/org/apache/tika/config/TikaConfigTest.java&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;/tika/trunk/tika-core/src/test/resources/org/apache/tika/config/&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-1653&quot; title=&quot;Tika config xml shouldn&amp;#39;t read nested parser definitions as top level&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;TIKA-1653&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;TIKA-1653&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-norepeat.xml&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;/tika/trunk/tika-parsers/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/parser/ctakes/CTAKESParser.java&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
